		                                            <span class="btn btn-default btn-xs s-genre" data-value="순발력">순발력</span>
		                                            <span class="btn btn-default btn-xs s-genre" data-value="가족">가족</span>
		                                            <span class="btn btn-default btn-xs s-genre" data-value="카드">카드</span>                                            
